# Government Tender Announcement

## Procurement Details

* **Reference Number:** cb-166-57945483
* **Solicitation Number:** 20232421-IRB
* **Publication Date:** January 22nd, 2024
* **Tender Closing Date:** January 31st, 2024 14:00:00 (Eastern Time)

## Summary

The Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada (IRB) is pleased to announce a Request for Proposal (RFP) No. 20232421-IRB, under the Temporary Help Services (THS) Procurement Arrangement. The RFP is issued to establish one contract with a reliable and skilled professional for a period of 240 days, from the contract award date to January 5th, 2025.

## Description of Work

The IRB requires temporary help services under the Procurement Services Categories (Stream 9) - Category 9.2 Procurement, under the THS method of supply, using the method of supply #1. The services are required to support the IRB's National Capital Region (NCR) office.

## Eligibility Criteria

This RFP is open to those Supply Arrangement Holders under the THS (Temporary Help Services) for the National Capital Region (NCR) who have qualified under the following categories:

* Stream 9: Category 9.2 Procurement (Senior)

## Security Requirements

* Common PS SRCL #06 applies
* Minimum Corporate Security Required: Designated Organization Screening (DOS)
* Minimum Resource Security Required: Reliability

## Tender Status

* **Tender Status:** Expired
* **Notice Type:** RFP against Supply Arrangement
* **Procurement Method:** Competitive - Selective tendering
* **Selection Criteria:** Highest Combined Rating of Technical Merit and Price

## Trade Agreements

The RFP is open to Tenderers under the following Trade Agreements:

* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on
